data.description: Welcome to this stunning split floor plan 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home nestled in the community of Copper Basin. Here, you'll find relaxation & an array of incredible community amenities just waiting for you to explore. With a community center, fitness center, community pool, & spa at your fingertips. Situated on a generously sized corner premium lot, this home offers both space and privacy. The tranquil park across the street adds to the appeal. Step inside to discover a like-new home featuring a calming color palette & an abundance of natural light. The beautiful tile t/o the main living areas creates a seamless flow. The open floor plan is perfect for entertaining & gatherings. The kitchen is a dream, featuring stainless steel appliances, elegant granite counters, & plenty of cabinetry for all your needs. The spacious 3 car tandem garage offers ample room for vehicles, storage, or even a workshop. Enjoy the convenience of being close to shopping, eateries, & entertainment options. Explore hiking trails & outdoor activities at the majestic San Tan Mountains, just a stone's throw away. This home offers a place to live & a lifestyle to cherish. Whether you're savoring quiet moments in your backyard, enjoying community amenities, or exploring the natural beauty of the San Tan Mountains, this property has it all at a fantastic price!
